    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> drained</strong> <strong>macaroni</strong> and <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> to the <strong>béchamel </strong>and mix well – this is your <strong>macaroni cheese</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>ragù </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> (or individual smaller ones) and top with the <strong>macaroni cheese</strong></p><p>Sprinkle the<strong> grated cheese </strong>over the top</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15 min or until bubbling and golden – this is your<strong> ragù bake</strong></p>",
