      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> remaining balsamic vinegar </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and toss through the <strong>rocket</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>ragù bake</strong> with the <strong>dressed rocket</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
